			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_RH-</LocID>								<Text>항적혈구 동종면역</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_RH-_DESCRIPTION</LocID>					<Text>동종면역은 유전적으로 다른 세포 및 조직과의 접촉 이후, 외부 항원을 대상으로 하는 면역 반응을 의미합니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_METRORRAGIE</LocID>						<Text>자궁출혈</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_METRORRAGIE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>월경주기 이외의 기간에 일어나는 혈액손실.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_RETARD_REGLE</LocID>						<Text>늦은 월경</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_RETARD_REGLE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>월경이 늦어지고 있습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_GROSSESSE</LocID>						<Text>임신</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_GROSSESSE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>임신 중인 상태입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HEMOPERITOINE</LocID>					<Text>복강내출혈</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HEMOPERITOINE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>		<Text>복막강 내에 혈액이 존재합니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>			
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HYPERANDROGEN</LocID>					<Text>생물학적 안드로겐과잉증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HYPERANDROGEN_DESCRIPTION</LocID>		<Text>여성에게서 발견되는 높은 안드로겐 수치.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_SEBORRHEE</LocID>						<Text>지루</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_SEBORRHEE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>비정상적으로 증가된 피지 분비량.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HIRSUTISME</LocID>						<Text>다모증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HIRSUTISME_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>여성의 통상적으로 체모가 적거나 없는 부위에 체모가 많이 나는 현상.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ACNE</LocID>								<Text>여드름</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ACNE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>					<Text>피부샘 및 모낭의 염증으로 발생하는 피부 트러블. 사춘기 때 많이 발견되며 보통 얼굴에 뾰루지 형태로 발견되곤 한다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ACANTHOSIS_NIGRICANS</LocID>				<Text>흑색극세포종</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ACANTHOSIS_NIGRICANS_DESCRIPTION</LocID>	<Text>몸의 접히는 부분 또는 주름이 (겨드랑이, 사타구니 또는 목 등) 어둡게 착색되거나 혹은 부드럽게 두꺼워지는 현상이 특징적인 피부 증상으로 비만, 인슐린 내성, 호르몬 불균형 또는 특정 약물 복용과 밀접되게 연관되어 있습니다. 흔치 않은 경우지만 암의 징후로 나타나기도 합니다(위암 또는 간암).</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_AMENORRHEE</LocID>						<Text>무월경증 </Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_AMENORRHEE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>비정상적인 월경의 멈춤 또는 줄어듦.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_BOUFFEE_VASOMOTRICE</LocID>				<Text>상기됨</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_BOUFFEE_VASOMOTRICE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>	<Text>상기된다는 것은 얼굴 또는 다른 피부가 다양한 생리학적 이유로 인하여 눈에 띄게 붉어지는 현상입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_SECHERESSE_VAGIN</LocID>					<Text>질 건조증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_SECHERESSE_VAGIN_DESCRIPTION</LocID>		<Text>질 건조증은 감소된 에스트로겐 수치로 인한 결과입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_DYSMENORRHEE</LocID>						<Text>월경통</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_DYSMENORRHEE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>월경이 고통스럽습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_MENORRAGIE</LocID>						<Text>월경 과다증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_MENORRAGIE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>비정상적으로 월경혈이 과다 분출됩니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_POLLAKIURIE</LocID>						<Text>빈뇨</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_POLLAKIURIE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>비정상적으로 자주 소변을 봅니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_LEUCORRHEE</LocID>						<Text>백대하</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_LEUCORRHEE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>점막의 염증 또는 충혈로 인해 질로부터 분비되는 희고 끈적거리는 분비물.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ULCERATION_GENITAL</LocID>				<Text>음부궤양</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ULCERATION_GENITAL_DESCRIPTION</LocID>	<Text>음부궤양은 생식기관에서 발견되는 단일 혹은 다수의 수포, 궤양 또는 까진 병변들로, 서혜부 림프절염을 동반하거나 그렇지 않을 수도 있고, 성병에 의한 감염을 의심해볼 수 있게 합니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_CHANCRE_SYPHILIS</LocID>					<Text>매독성 경성하감</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_CHANCRE_SYPHILIS_DESCRIPTION</LocID>		<Text>매독으로 인한 주된 궤양으로, 통증이 없으며, 가장자리가 딱딱하게 굳고 피부가 벗겨진 발진입니다. 감염 경로 부근에 발생합니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_PREMATURE</LocID>						<Text>조산의</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_PREMATURE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>조산으로, 또는 관련되거나, 징후가 보이거나 함으로 내원하게 되었습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HPV_HR</LocID>							<Text>고위험성 HPV</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HPV_HR_DESCRIPTION</LocID>				<Text>고위험성 HPV는 정상세포들을 비정상적인 세포로 변이시킬 수 있습니다. 이 비정상적인 세포들은 오랜 시간에 걸쳐 암세포로 변이할 수 있습니다. 고위험성 HPV는 주로 자궁경부의 세포들에 영향을 주지만, 질, 외음부, 직장, 음경, 입, 목 등에서도 암을 일으킬 수 있습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_DOULEUR_PELV</LocID>						<Text>골반통</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_DOULEUR_PELV_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>골반 부위에서 느껴지는 통증입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_COL_ROUGE</LocID>						<Text>충혈된 자궁경부</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_COL_ROUGE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>검사 중 자궁 경부가 붉게 충혈되어 있습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_VEGETATION_KYSTE</LocID>					<Text>낭포외적 증식증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_VEGETATION_KYSTE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>		<Text>초음파 영상에서 발견된 증식물입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_TUMEFACTION</LocID>						<Text>가슴 붓기</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_TUMEFACTION_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>비정상적인 유방의 팽창입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_MASSE_HOMOGENE</LocID>					<Text>균일성 종괴</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_MASSE_HOMOGENE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>		<Text>초음파 영상에서 발견된 균일성 종괴입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_CONTRACTION_UTERINE</LocID>				<Text>협착 골반</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_CONTRACTION_UTERINE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>	<Text>골반의 폭 또는 너비가 감소해 정상적인 분만이 어려운 경우입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ODEUR_VAGINALE</LocID>					<Text>질향</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ODEUR_VAGINALE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>		<Text>강렬한 "생선"같은 질의 냄새입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_POST_PARTUM</LocID>						<Text>산욕기</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_POST_PARTUM_DESCRIPTION</LocID>			<Text>출산 직후 또는 이후의 상태입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>

			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_AXILLARY_LYMPH_NODES</LocID>								<Text>겨드랑이 림프절</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_INGUINAL_LYMPH_NODES</LocID>								<Text>서혜부 림프절</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_SUPRACLAVICULAR_LYMPH_NODES</LocID>						<Text>쇄골상 림프절</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
	
		
	



			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HYPOKALIEMIE</LocID>										<Text>저칼륨혈증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HYPOKALIEMIE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>							<Text>혈청 칼륨 농도가 정상 이하로 떨어진 상태입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HYPERKALIEMIE</LocID>									<Text>고칼륨혈증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HYPERKALIEMIE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>						<Text>혈청 칼륨 농도가 정상 이상으로 과도하게 상승했습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_OAP</LocID>												<Text>폐부종</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_OAP_DESCRIPTION</LocID>									<Text>폐에 체액이 과도하게 쌓여 호흡곤란을 야기하는 상태입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ABOLITION_POULS</LocID>									<Text>맥박 없음</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ABOLITION_POULS_DESCRIPTION</LocID>						<Text>환자의 맥박이 없습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_MARBRURE</LocID>											<Text>망상청피반</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_MARBRURE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>								<Text>피부에 그물 모양의 청자색 반이 형성되는 질환으로, 다른 질환과 동반되어 나타나기도 합니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_POUL_HYPERPULSE</LocID>									<Text>반동 맥박</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_POUL_HYPERPULSE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>						<Text>크고 강하게 뛰는 맥박입니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_TURJESCENCE_JUGULAIRE</LocID>							<Text>목정맥 팽창</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_TURJESCENCE_JUGULAIRE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>				<Text>목정맥이 눈에 띄게 튀어나온 상태로, 우심실의 기능 이상을 의미합니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_REFLUX_HJ</LocID>										<Text>간목정맥 역류</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_REFLUX_HJ_DESCRIPTION</LocID>							<Text>복부 중앙을 강하게 눌렀을 때 목정맥압(JVP)이 지속적으로 상승했습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HEPATALGIE</LocID>										<Text>간통증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HEPATALGIE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>							<Text>환자가 간에 통증을 느낍니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_SOUFFLE_ABDOMINAL</LocID>								<Text>복부 잡음</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_SOUFFLE_ABDOMINAL_DESCRIPTION</LocID>					<Text>복부 소음의 존재는 복부 대동맥류 존재 또는 신장 동맥의 협착을 반영할 수 있습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_SOUFFLE_VASCULAIRE</LocID>								<Text>혈관 잡음</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_SOUFFLE_VASCULAIRE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>					<Text/>	</GameDBLocalizedString>

