			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_MACROGLOSSIA_DESCRIPTION</LocID>								<Text>환자의 혀가 비정상적으로 커졌습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HYPOGLYCEMIA</LocID>											<Text>저혈당증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HYPOGLYCEMIA_DESCRIPTION</LocID>								<Text>혈당이 정상보다 낮습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_GYNECOMASTIA</LocID>											<Text>여성형 유방</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_GYNECOMASTIA_DESCRIPTION</LocID>								<Text>남성의 유방이 여성의 유방처럼 발달했습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ATROPHIE_TESTICULE</LocID>									<Text>고환 위축</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_ATROPHIE_TESTICULE_DESCRIPTION</LocID>						<Text>고환의 크기가 감소했습니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_DRY_SKIN</LocID>												<Text>건조한 피부</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_DRY_SKIN_DESCRIPTION</LocID>									<Text>환자의 피부가 건조합니다.</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
			<GameDBLocalizedString>	<LocID>SYM_CRP_HYPERPRL</LocID>												<Text>고프로락틴혈증</Text>	</GameDBLocalizedString>
